== 迴響 ==
《危機女王》獲得多為負面的評價，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]32%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/our_brand_is_crisis_2016/|title=Our Brand is Crisis (2015)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=November 1, 2015|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125051107/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/our_brand_is_crisis_2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分51<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/our-brand-is-crisis-2015|title=Our Brand Is Crisis reviews|website=Metacritic|accessdate=October 30, 2015|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926193916/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/our-brand-is-crisis-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>；據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾從「A+」至「F」之間給出了「C+」的評價<ref name="deadline">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/bradley-cooper-sandra-bullock-burnt-our-brand-is-crisis-the-martian-scouts-guide-halloween-box-office-1201595523/ |title=Bradley Cooper, ‘The Martian’ To Scare Away Sandra Bullock & ‘Scouts’ At Halloween B.O. – Preview |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2015-11-02 |archive-date=2015-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031064034/http://deadline.com/2015/10/bradley-cooper-sandra-bullock-burnt-our-brand-is-crisis-the-martian-scouts-guide-halloween-box-office-1201595523/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影首周票房收入僅320萬美元，排名當周第八，成為布拉克職業生涯最低的首周成績，甚至低於1996年的《[[偷心計畫|偷心計畫]]》（470萬美元）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/sandra-bullock-bradley-cooper-box-office-bomb-our-brand-is-crisis-burnt-1201600750/ |title=Star-Driven Casualties ‘Our Brand Is Crisis’ & ‘Burnt’ At The B.O.: What The Hell Happened? |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2015-11-02 |archive-date=2015-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118112328/http://deadline.com/2015/10/sandra-bullock-bradley-cooper-box-office-bomb-our-brand-is-crisis-burnt-1201600750/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；與起初預計的500萬至700萬美元的預測相差甚遠<ref name="deadline"/>。

